	(text "Input and output capacitors are selected as recommended. \nThe inductor is selected based on recomended parts as well. \nRecommended combination Cout = 10uF and L = 4.7uH. \nCin is recommended as 10uF and can be scaled up as neccessary. \n\nInductor: \n4.7 µH Shielded Drum Core, Wirewound Inductor 1.1 A 270mOhm Max 1008 (2520 Metric) Flat Wire"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 299.974 32.766 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "29da0527-76e2-4ce1-a4e1-e38f0ea3980b")
	)
	(text "https://www.digikey.co.uk/en/products/detail/texas-instruments/TPS62745DSSR/5356699?_gl=1*dqki3q*_up*MQ..*_gs*MQ..&gclid=CjwKCAiAoNbIBhB5EiwAZFbYGDQMrLkmMOXL8TdX7OnnJf9H8Laiof7K57_SplWZce2CO4fqjUSg4hoC3_QQAvD_BwE&gclsrc=aw.ds&gbraid=0AAAAADrbLlgXA-mWhUkXmO3Qwz8L3DPir"
