	)
	(text "TP62745\nThis chip features high efficienncy between 80-90 percent at low currents compare to others. \nThe chip feature programmable voltage output and reduces component count.\n\n0000 on VSEL1/2/3/4 provides 1.8V. \n\n1.8V selected to provide 0.2V overheads to the supply voltages for the DAC to reduce chances of clipping."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 299.72 18.034 0)
